fusioninventory-agent (1:2.4-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release
  * Updated debian support:
    - Fix default configuration to make system logging the default with LOG_DAEMON
      facility
    - Fix default configuration to activate new "include" directive: users should
      now create a .cfg file in /etc/fusioninventory/conf.d to tune agent
      configuration to their needs, at least server option.
    - Prox::PID::File dependency removed
    - Removed mo more needed cron tasks

